data.description: Country living awaits! Spacious and well maintained, 2018 Palm Harbor Manufactured Home on 7 fenced acres. Detached 2 Car Garage, 43x76 covered area with partial concrete including a full RV hook up that could easily be made into your dream home or mancave with additional parking! There is also an additional Barn at the front of the property and loafing shed for horses or other livestock. Home features covered porches on both front and back.
